reg_info.act_under: Woodlands Improvement Act   Loi sur l’amélioration des terrains boisés

content.content: 1. The parts of Ontario described in the Schedules to Appendix A are designated as private forest management areas, each to be known by the name in the heading of the Schedule. R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 1100, s. 1.

content.content: 6. A reference in this Regulation to the Schedules to Appendix A, B, C, D or E, is a reference to the Schedules to Appendix A, B, C, D or E, as the case may be, in Regulation 948 of the Revised Regulations of Ontario, 1980, as that Schedule read on the day before the coming into force of the Revised Regulations of Ontario, 1990. R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 1100, s. 6.
